    - rid: 107151359355650164
      type: {class: WeighedChoice, ns: , asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        modules:
        - weight: 50
          module:
          - rid: 107151359355650165
          output: 'Though the price is steep, can one truly place a value upon talent?
            The prodigy accepts us as his new benefactors, and our priests are already
            planning his first commission. Our sacred truths shall take form through
            the hands of this youth. Through his art, we find immortality!

            [Gained
            40 Zeal & Boon]

'
        - weight: 40
          module:
          - rid: 107151359355650166
          - rid: 107151359355650167
          output: 'Curse it! Another sect outbid us, offering a sum far greater than
            what we had planned. It does not appear we shall be able to recruit the
            lad now. Our fold is devastated by the missed chance.

            [Gained
            50 Wealth Lost 15 Bliss]

'
        - weight: 10
          module:
          - rid: 107151359355650168
          - rid: 107151359355650169
          - rid: 107151359355650170
          - rid: 107151359355650171
          output: 'Grave trouble! The artist took offense at "men of God attempting
            to purchase his spirit." It seems his zeal for the Beholder outweighs
            his reason! Oh, what a loss... and worse still, he has vowed that his
            next masterpiece shall be a depiction of our sins. What calamity!

            [Gained
            50 Wealth Lost 30 Zeal, 10 Bliss & 20 Flock]

'
